		{
			description: ["An AE2 Meteorite crash-lands somewhere in every world — the crater contains Certus Quartz Ore and, at the center, a Mysterious Cube holding the Inscriber Press blueprints needed to advance into Applied Energistics 2 automation. Use an Explorer's Compass to locate the nearest meteorite before spending hours searching manually."]
