		{
			description: ["YUNG's Better Mineshafts replaces vanilla mineshafts with biome-specific variants — dripstone, lush, desert, and jungle variants each have unique visual themes and loot configurations. Planks support the tunnel ceilings; cave-ins and rail bridges connect cavern floors. Minecart chests inside contain ores, rails, and occasionally Name Tags."]
			id: "B001000000000001"
