		{
			description: ["YUNG's Better Strongholds vastly expands the vanilla stronghold with additional rooms, decorative halls, prison corridors, and a fully-realized End Portal chamber. The library within holds some of the best enchanted book loot in the early game. Silverfish spawn aggressively when you approach the portal room — come prepared with AoE capability."]
			id: "B001000000000002"
