		{
			description: ["YUNG's Better Dungeons replaces vanilla dungeon spawners with elaborated multi-room structures. Spider dens, undead crypts, and standard dungeons each have themed layouts, traps, and loot configurations that go well beyond the vanilla chest-and-spawner design. The spawner itself can be deactivated or repurposed as an XP farm."]
			id: "B001000000000003"
