		{
			description: ["YUNG's Better Desert Temples replace the vanilla pyramid with a multi-floor structure of booby-trapped corridors, hidden vaults, and TNT-laden floors. Disarm rather than detonate — the TNT room contains valuable loot below the pressure plate puzzle. Sand-colored floors hide the drop into the main chamber."]
			id: "B001000000000004"
