		{
			description: ["YUNG's Better Jungle Temples are expanded into multi-room structures with elaborate puzzles using dispensers, pistons, and tripwires. The original temple had two chests; the upgraded version has multiple treasure vaults behind escalating puzzle complexity. Bring a pickaxe — some shortcuts cut through the puzzle walls entirely."]
			id: "B001000000000005"
