		{
			description: ["YUNG's Better Ocean Monuments transform the vanilla prismarine fortress into a genuine multi-wing dungeon. An Elder Guardian guards the treasure vault; three more patrol the wings. Mining fatigue blocks digging — come with either Milk Buckets to cure it, or enough combat power to clear it fast. Sponge rooms are now multiple layers deep."]
