		{
			description: ["YUNG's Better Nether Fortresses expand the vanilla fortress into a multi-section structure with proper entrance gates, throne rooms, and dedicated Blaze spawner chambers. Wither Skeletons remain the primary dangerous occupant. The fortress connects to attached Nether pathways and occasionally has secondary towers visible from a distance."]
