		{
			description: ["When Dungeons Arise scatters large, heavily decorated structures across the overworld — abandoned temples, fortified mansions, pirate ships, and coliseums. The Abandoned Temple features multi-floor layouts with mob spawners, traps, and high-value loot chests. Many WDA structures contain unique loot tables that include weapons and armor above what vanilla structures offer."]
