			description: ["The WDA Infested Temple is smaller than the Abandoned Temple but more densely packed with spawners. Spider-themed interior layout with web-covered corridors and hidden passages. Useful for locating early silk and string in bulk; the central chamber holds a trapped treasure cache worth the combat encounter."]
