			dependencies: ["B001000000000008"]
			description: ["The WDA Undead Pirate Ship is a spectral galleon beached or floating on water, crewed by skeleton pirates. The ship holds nautical-themed loot including maps, compasses, and naval equipment. Multiple decks provide unique combat encounters; the captain's quarters on the upper deck contain the primary loot cache."]
