		{
			description: ["Terralith adds spires — natural rock pillars that rise dramatically above the landscape, decorated with vegetation and mineral deposits. The Frosted Dungeon generates underground in cold biomes and contains unique ice-themed loot. Terralith's fortified villages are larger than vanilla, with stone walls and multiple professions clustered inside."]
