			description: ["Structory adds hand-crafted small structures scattered across biomes — ruins, shrines, tents, and watchtowers. They rarely have spawners but often contain buried loot caches or unique small chests. Structory Towers are more combat-focused vertical structures with mob-occupied floors and a rooftop reward."]
