		{
			description: ["Buried Treasure spawns beneath beaches and underwater near shipwrecks. A Treasure Map from a shipwreck chest or cartographer villager marks the X precisely. The cache always contains a Heart of the Sea, which is required to craft the Conduit — a powerful underwater breathing and combat structure."]
