		{
			description: ["Shipwrecks wash up on beaches and sink to ocean floors across the world. Three hold chests — supply chest (food and tools), treasure chest (gold, iron, emeralds), and map chest (treasure map, compass). Drowned spawn near or inside submerged wrecks. A full wreck loot run provides a significant early-game resource boost."]
